features: 【Adorable and Creative Design】Our aesthetic ballpoint pens are simply irresistible! Featuring five cat color combinations, each with its own unique expression, these kawaii gel pens are incredibly cute, creative, and one-of-a-kind. The delightful cat's paw pattern adds a touch of fun and instantly captures attention, making your writing experience more enjoyable.

【Convenient Cat Paw Pen Clip】With the cute cat pen clip, you can easily attach these pens to books, bags, or pockets, ensuring they're always within reach. The charming cat's paws peeking out from your book page create a soft and cute visual, offering a delightful way to decompress and express your inner girl's heart. Perfect as a gift for little girls, teenagers, or professional women alike.

【Comfortable Smooth Grip】Our cute cat ballpoint pens boast a delicate and charming plastic case that exudes uniqueness and sophistication. The elastic touch and comfortable grip ensure you can write for extended periods without experiencing fatigue. Whether you're taking notes in class or jotting down ideas, these kawaii pens make an excellent back to school gift.

【Quick Drying Ink】This black ink gel pen features a 0.5mm bullet nib that allows for precise and detailed drawings. The quick-drying ink ensures immediate drying, preventing unsightly smudges and enabling you to create clearer, more defined artwork. Enjoy the smooth and continuous ink flow that requires minimal pressure to achieve crisp lines.

【Retractable Rollerball Pens】Say goodbye to lost pen caps and the hassle of constantly removing and replacing them! Our fine point pens are designed with a retractable feature, simply press the cap and the pen tip automatically retracts for easy storage and convenience. The satisfying click response provides a gratifying sensory experience, which can help relieve stress and ignite your creativity.

reviews.reviewText: did I need pens with cat paws? No. did I have to have them?yesThese are so cute. They have little cat paws on them and the top of the barrel is a darker shade to the bottom of the barrel, with the exception of the brown pen. the brown colored pen has a black top.These pens click and so you can make sure that when you’re done using them, to click again so the pen nib goes back up into the barrel. These actually feel really nice in the hand and they have a smooth feel to them. The cat paw is a very soft silicone material that provides some comfort while I’m writing.This is a gel pen, and the ink is black. It writes really smoothly without smudging. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Kěài (or Kawaii, if you prefer the Japanese term) toe-bean pens!!!
reviews.reviewText: The packaging designer did a spectacular job. The box has a cute cat theme. When you open it, you see a paw/toe-bean tab. Pull the tab and the insert holding the pens slides out (see photo).The pen has a very fine tip (like my go-to black pen, the Uniball Signo Micro 207) and moves smoothly across the page. The ink is a dark black and dries reasonably fast (though not as fast as the Uniball's). The body is made from a soft-touch plastic, the cap from a regular (hard touch) plastic. The feel in hand is acceptable (not as nice as the Uniball).In summary: they are very cute, work perfectly well, and are quite cute.Disclosure: I received this item for free. My review is honest and uncensored by the seller.
